DTSTAMP:20260724T124428Z
SUMMARY:Mindvalley Awards Ceremony — FULL VIDEO TEAM (timing still TBC on source)
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Tallinn:20260724T180000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Tallinn:20260724T190000
LOCATION:Main Stage (Black Box)
DESCRIPTION:Status: TENTATIVE\nWho: Gareth Winter\, Kaitlin O'Toole\, Khairul Johari\, Nadir Salam\, Kuhan Kunasegaran\nPer Fisher (voice note\, 13 Jul): this needs the full production team's focus\, not passive coverage — many speakers fly in specifically for the video/photo opportunity here\, and a strong asset can lift a speaker's fee by 10–20k. Plan wide shots + a rehearsed handheld move (reference: the Lynda piece Kuhan shot handheld) rather than one static camera. Only 1hr — crew is free from 4pm that day (Jeffrey Allen MC/assets wrap by 4). CREW CONFIRMED (13 Jul): full core team (Khairul\, Nadir\, Kuhan) + Gareth — they're all already on-site for the awards\, working together\, so no separate resourcing needed. Kaitlin O'Toole hosting. Only open item is the exact timing on the source sheet (see ch-mv-awards-timing).\nFull schedule: https://garethwinter-cpu.github.io/mindvalley-u-production/
END:VEVENT
