DESCRIPTION:Who: Marisa Peer\, Rachel Pringle\, Khairul Johari\nCONFIRMED (Matt\, 21 Jul): Rachel Pringle Urb (arrives 29th) on Marisa's "Your Mind\, Your Rules" podcast\, Fri 31 Jul 4:00–5:30pm (90 min). Slots into the open Energiakeskus afternoon after Lee Holden's interview wraps (15:30)\, with a 30-min reset. Marisa free after her 12:45 assets\; Rachel free all day. Unit 1 (Khairul) free by then. Both women — one 60-min makeup call at 15:00. Last studio session of the run.\nFull schedule: https://garethwinter-cpu.github.io/mindvalley-u-production/
